Greynolds Park Golf Course- Directions/ Park Entry
Please note:
The physical address location navigates you into the park from
W. Dixie Highway
, that entry is
only accessible after 9am
during weekdays from Monday to Friday. Weekends
after sunrise.
The alternate entry point is at the intersection of
Miami Gardens Drive and NE 22 Ave
.
However, there is no specific physical address available for input on GPS navigation.
